<!-- ARCHITECTURE -->
<section id="architecture">
<div class="container">
<div class="sec-label">System Architecture</div>
<h2 class="sec-title">从采集到验证，五层验证链路</h2>
<p class="sec-desc">不是AI工具，是AI获客的验证基础设施。每层解决一个具体问题。</p>
<div class="arch-layers" style="max-width:720px">
<div class="arch-layer"><span class="arch-ico"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 12.55a11 11 0 0 1 14.08 0"/><path d="M1.42 9a16 16 0 0 1 21.16 0"/><path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/><circle cx="12" cy="20" r="1"/></svg></span><div style="flex:1"><div class="arch-lname">L0 Capture Layer</div><div class="arch-value">识别ChatGPT/DeepSeek/豆包等AI平台的推荐流量 <span style="color:var(--text2)">· 识别率（验证期目标95%）</span></div></div></div>
<div style="padding:2px 0 2px 30px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:var(--blue);font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono)">→ 推荐流量信号 →</div>
<div class="arch-layer"><span class="arch-ico"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg></span><div style="flex:1"><div class="arch-lname">L1 Attribution Engine</div><div class="arch-value">每条AI内容生成唯一action_id，从点击到成交全链路追踪 <span style="color:var(--text2)">· 追踪准确率（验证期目标98%）</span></div></div></div>
<div style="padding:2px 0 2px 30px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:var(--blue);font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono)">→ action_id信号 →</div>
<div class="arch-layer"><span class="arch-ico"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><div style="flex:1"><div class="arch-lname">L2 Verification Engine</div><div class="arch-value">确认成交真实发生，排除刷单和误归因 <span style="color:var(--green);font-weight:600">· 验证准确率99%</span></div></div></div>
<div style="padding:2px 0 2px 30px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:var(--blue);font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono)">→ 验证事件信号 →</div>
<div class="arch-layer"><span class="arch-ico"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg></span><div style="flex:1"><div class="arch-lname">L3 Optimization Engine</div><div class="arch-value">基于验证结果，优化GEO内容和投放策略 <span style="color:var(--text2)">· AI引用率+32%</span></div></div></div>
<div style="padding:2px 0 2px 30px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:var(--blue);font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono)">→ 优化策略信号 →</div>
<div class="arch-layer"><span class="arch-ico"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M2 15c6.667-6 13.333 0 20-6"/><path d="M9 22c1.798-1.998 2.518-3.995 2.807-5.993"/><path d="M15 2c-1.798 1.998-2.518 3.995-2.807 5.993"/><path d="M2 9c6.667 6 13.333 0 20 6"/></svg></span><div style="flex:1"><div class="arch-lname">L4 Business Twin</div><div class="arch-value">经营数字孪生，模拟决策预测ROI变化 <span style="color:var(--green);font-weight:600">· ROI模拟偏差&lt;8%</span></div></div></div>

